tor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9a7e951 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9a7e951\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n<p>Esas olarak insan ta\u015f\u0131nmas\u0131n\u0131 ama\u00e7layan konfor ve kullan\u0131m rahatl\u0131\u011f\u0131 \u00f6n planda tutulmu\u015f asans\u00f6rlerdir.<\/p>\n<p>\u0130nsan asans\u00f6rleri; konutlarda 240 kg\u2019 dan 1000 kg\u2019a kadar insan ta\u015f\u0131mak i\u00e7in kullan\u0131lan ve konut d\u0131\u015f\u0131 yerlerde(otel, hastane, i\u015f merkezi) 630 kg\u2019 dan 1600 kg\u2019a kadar insan ve\/veya y\u00fck ta\u015f\u0131mak ama\u00e7l\u0131 olarak tasarlanan asans\u00f6rlerdir. 3 ila 21 ki\u015filik kapasiteye kadar yap\u0131labilen insan asans\u00f6rlerinin anma h\u0131zlar\u0131 da binan\u0131n y\u00fcksekli\u011fine g\u00f6re de\u011fi\u015fken bir \u015fekilde 0,40 m\/sn ile 2.5 m\/sn h\u0131zlar\u0131 aras\u0131nda de\u011fi\u015febilir.<\/p>\n<p>\u0130nsan asans\u00f6rleri, binalar\u0131n projelendirmesi a\u015famas\u0131nda yap\u0131lan trafik hesaplar\u0131na ve avan projelerine uygun olarak imal edilip, yerlerine monte edilir.Projelendirme safhas\u0131ndan imalat ve montaj a\u015famas\u0131n\u0131n sonuna kadar t\u00fcm kademeler, uzman ekiplerimiz taraf\u0131ndan kontrol edilerek, son kullan\u0131c\u0131ya en uygun hale getirilir.<\/p>\n<p>Asans\u00f6r talebinize ve asans\u00f6r kuyusuna uygun olarak;<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b499e69 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b499e69\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n<ul>\n<li>Tam otomatik teleskopik veya merkezden a\u00e7\u0131lan kat kap\u0131s\u0131 se\u00e7enekleri<\/li>\n<li>Tam otomatik teleskopik veya merkezden a\u00e7\u0131lan kabin kap\u0131s\u0131 se\u00e7enekleri<\/li>\n<li>\u00c7ift h\u0131z veya VVVF frekans kontroll\u00fc kademesiz h\u0131z se\u00e7enekleri<\/li>\n<li>Tam elektronik mikroi\u015flemci kontroll\u00fc normal kumandal\u0131 veya sellektif toplamal\u0131, simpleks veya grup kumanda se\u00e7enekleri<\/li>\n<li>Opsiyonel olarak acil kata getirme sistemi<\/li>\n<li>Kabin dekoratifleri; paslanmaz ile orijinal tasar\u0131ml\u0131 laminant\u0131n m\u00fckemmel uyumu olan l\u00fcks fosformik veya desenli paslanmaz \u00e7elik kaplamal\u0131 duvar se\u00e7eneklerine sahiptir.<\/li>\n<li>Linolyum, mermer, seramik veya granit taban se\u00e7eneklerine sahiptir.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-53eb6e2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"53eb6e2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n<p>B\u00fct\u00fcn bunlar\u0131n d\u0131\u015f\u0131nda sizin i\u00e7in tasarlanm\u0131\u015f, size \u00f6zel \u00e7\u00f6z\u00fcmler; \u00f6zel paslanmaz desenler, vitray, cam panelli kap\u0131lar, panoramik kabinler gibi bir\u00e7ok se\u00e7enek bulunmaktad\u0131r.<\/p>\n<p><b>Dikkat! \u0130nsan asans\u00f6r\u00fcn\u00fcz\u00fc mutlaka, Tekin As Asans\u00f6r taraf\u0131ndan periyodik ve genel asans\u00f6r bak\u0131m\u0131 yapt\u0131r\u0131lmal\u0131d\u0131r. \u0130nsan hayat\u0131 her \u015feyden \u00f6nemli ve de\u011ferlidir.<\/b><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u0130nsan (Yolcu) Asans\u00f6r\u00fc Esas olarak insan ta\u015f\u0131nmas\u0131n\u0131 ama\u00e7layan konfor ve kullan\u0131m rahatl\u0131\u011f\u0131 \u00f6n planda tutulmu\u015f asans\u00f6rlerdir. \u0130nsan asans\u00f6rleri; konutlarda 240 kg\u2019 dan 1000 kg\u2019a kadar insan ta\u015f\u0131mak i\u00e7in kullan\u0131lan ve konut d\u0131\u015f\u0131 yerlerde(otel, hast